			dependencies: ["59F498EBB5FE2C2C"]
			description: ["Drawer Controllers will search for any connected drawer within 12 blocks, and then expose all of those drawers as a large combined inventory. This lets you hook up a single pipe, tube, duct, spark, storage bus, etc. and interact with the entire bank of drawers."]
