		{
			dependencies: ["2DA77E139D3C1C64"]
			description: [
				"The Melter acts as a 1-block compact version of the smeltery, and can be powered by a heater or a seared tank. Both the Melter and the Smeltery are much more efficient at melting down ores and armor, yielding more metal than furnaces would. "
				""
				"The basics of this machine can be found in &oPuny Smelting&r, which can be crafted with crafting a book with grout. "
			]
			id: "2F26A57E50C8E4BC"
			rewards: [
