		{
			dependencies: ["3EE16F0264052C50"]
			description: ["Welcome to Tinkers' Construct! This mod completely overhauls Minecraft's original tool system, and adds a variety of other content. In order to get started, you'll want to follow along with the book &oMaterials and You&r. The book will walk you through general gameplay mechanics, the first tier of materials you have immediate access to, some primitive tools you can make and how to get ahold of the next books. "]
